<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>现拌鲜吃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>传统美食</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆里的味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样的火车站赵姥姥热卤现拌</p>
